    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><strong>My Very First Octopress Blog</strong></p>

<p>How to blog with Octopress:</p>

<ol>
  <li>
    <p>Generate a new post:
<div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>rake new_post[“Hello world”]
</span><span class='line'># create source/_post/2013-07-08-Hello-world.markdown</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div></p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Edit the new post with your favorite editor, i.e. vim.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Generate the page, preview and deploy to github:
<div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>rake generate
</span><span class='line'>rake preview
</span><span class='line'>rake deploy</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div></p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>commit the source:
<div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>git add .
</span><span class='line'>git commit -m ‘update message’
</span><span class='line'>git push origin source</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div></p>
  </li>
</ol>

<p>Some tips:</p>

<h3 id="codeblock">CodeBlock</h3>
<p><code>Codeblock</code> will plug formatted codes into your blog.
Syntex</p>

<pre><code>&lt;% codeblock [title] [lang:language] [url] [link text] %&gt;
code snippet
&lt;% endcodeblock %&gt;
</code></pre>
]]></content>
